REG NO: 86158


				About the SpaDe
.

		Space & Development Company Limited (SpaDe) is a company based in Dar es Salaam, Incorporated under the (Tanzanian) Companies Act of 2002 with registration number 86158. SpaDe provides consultancy services on land use/master planning, Geo Information through application of remote sensing and GIS, natural resource management, social engagement and out-grower capacity building on those technical areas of its operations. The company also facilitates land acquisition for investments, land related investment conflict resolution as well as providing Out-grower development services and rural value chains enhancement services for smallholder farmers and allied actors.





